  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "refId": "RV10-188:1",
      "text": "translated by"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "refId": "RV10-188:2",
      "text": "1. Now send ye Jatavedas forth, send hitherward the vigorous Steed"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "refId": "RV10-188:3",
      "text": "To seat him on our sacred grass."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "refId": "RV10-188:4",
      "text": "2. I raise the lofty eulogy of Jatavedas, raining boons,"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "refId": "RV10-188:5",
      "text": "With sages for his hero band."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "refId": "RV10-188:6",
      "text": "3. With flames of Jatavedas which carry oblation to the Gods,"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "refId": "RV10-188:7",
      "text": "May he promote our sacrifice."
    }
  ]
}
